caption: Bid Security
created: 20260405120000000
modified: 20260405120000000
title: Policy3330(III)(5)
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

When, in the judgment of the Superintendent, bid security is advisable, all bids must be accompanied by security in one of the following forms - certified check, cashier's check, personal money order, letter of credit or bid bond. The requirement for, and the amount of, the security must be set forth in the bid advertisement. All security presented must show the "Regional School District 8" as the payee.
